<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Forgot Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 20px 0 0 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="https://phamthanhnam.com"><img
                src="https://api.phamthanhnam.com/image/n/20230423-logo-1682242032133.png" class="logo"></a>
        <h1>Forgot Password</h1>
        <p>We've received a request to reset the password for your account on Pham Thanh Nam.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>To reset your password, click on the following link:</p>
        <a href="<%= link %>">Reset Password</a>
        <p>This link will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at ptnde18@gmail.com.</p>
        <p>Thanks,</p>
        <p>The Pham Thanh Nam Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>